00:43:21.219 --> 00:43:23.300
and need just a little support,

00:43:23.300 --> 00:43:28.020
I recently created this site called rstudio.com champion,

00:43:28.060 --> 00:43:30.379
but pulls together a lot of resources

00:43:30.379 --> 00:43:32.060
from people like you all,

00:43:32.979 --> 00:43:35.580
who have spoke at meetups and hangouts

00:43:35.580 --> 00:43:38.100
and just shares what people have been doing.

