and I think this was towards the very beginning

00:46:21.860 --> 00:46:24.300
of the presentation that said,

00:46:24.300 --> 00:46:27.340
when you mentioned the vanilla code,

00:46:27.340 --> 00:46:29.500
is it possible to discuss about it here?

00:46:30.860 --> 00:46:32.580
Vanilla code?

00:46:32.580 --> 00:46:34.340
I can't recall.

