So what we can do is we can have a function call as a text.

00:56:59.020 --> 00:57:02.100
So imagine, like, you know, if it is, you know,

00:57:02.100 --> 00:57:05.979
an environment variable in R with the sys.getEnv,

00:57:05.979 --> 00:57:08.459
and there it is, the environment variable.

00:57:10.179 --> 00:57:11.860
So these then become promises.

00:57:11.860 --> 00:57:14.300
So you can imagine you have a configuration file

00:57:14.300 --> 00:57:16.419
that tells where the data is

00:57:16.419 --> 00:57:19.020
