00:57:22.260 --> 00:57:24.139
And that is the promise that says,

00:57:24.139 --> 00:57:26.739
when you run this command, this environment variable

00:57:26.739 --> 00:57:29.739
or this key is going to be present in the environment.

00:57:29.739 --> 00:57:31.620
